('Berehynia', 'HAT-P-15', 0, '', 63, 'Berehynia was a Slavic deity of waters and riverbanks but in more recent times her status has been promoted to that of a national goddess — \"hearth mother, protectress of the earth\".', 'Ukrainian', '2019 IAU100 NameExoWorlds', 'Perseus', '2019/12/17', 119),
