('Dombay', 'HAT-P-3', 0, '', 83, 'Dombay is a resort region in the North Caucasus mountains that is enclosed by mountain forests and rich wildlife, including bears (as this star lies in the constellation Ursa Major, the great bear).', 'Russian', '2019 IAU100 NameExoWorlds', '', '2019/12/17', 137),
